        title: "Search Black-Owned and Diversity-Focused Home Care Agencies",
        content: "Look for Black-owned home care agencies in your city by searching Black-owned home care near me or asking at your local church, senior center, or NAACP chapter. The National Caucus and Center on Black Aging at ncba-aging.org lists Black senior service providers across the country. The Better Business Bureau and Medicare's Home Health Compare tool at medicare.gov/care-compare let you check ratings on any agency. Many large national agencies such as BAYADA, Visiting Angels, and Right at Home also have strong diversity programs in specific cities. Make a list of three or four agencies that look promising.",
